description: Meet Kace, a brown-haired 21 year-old with a boy-next-door look and a well-built body, thanks to his love of running. He recently move further out west looking for a much more relaxed and friendly living environment. He doesn't date much, but he aspires to travel the world and form a successful career in day trading. “People would describe my personality as very aggressive, some may say I’m cocky, others may say I’m confident. Most people would say I’m driven; I really know what I want to do I life. That’s just me.”
title: Kace
